description:
Feels like real life Mario Kart! 🚗🍄
Have you Ever driven up the California coast?
I recommend if you just hop in the car & drive up PCH 1!! Now that Hawaii requests vaccination records for travel other states & countries will begin to follow suit!  So if you've never gotten a passport or traveled much, I recommend you start doing it now Travel will be limited more and more as time goes on you don't want to look back and realize you never did the things you dreamed & talked about!  As I have been mentioning they will require mandatory vaccines which are going to have an RFID chip that will track you're temperature, location, and finances! 
MONDAY MOTIVATION - Dont let life pass you by!! ⛰⌛
